  "remarks": "Former Ambassador to Chad under Qadhafi regime. Responsible for implementing regime’s violent and repressive policies through recruitment of mercenaries, in conjunction with Muammar Qadhafi’s most trusted aides.\nDesignated for a travel ban by UNSC Resolution 1970 (2011); Listing: Designated under the Autonomous Sanctions Regulations 2011 on 2 March 2012. Formerly listed on the RBA Consolidated List as 2011LBY0018. Instrument of first designation and declaration: Autonomous Sanctions (Designated Persons and Entities and Declared Persons – Libya) List 2012 [F2012L00481]\nRelisting on 12 January 2024.",
